html:
Slimy, twisting maggot
In an office full of vials
Next to a woman-potato
Says "NO" to you
Then walks away in silence
Ignoring your words
Gets into an electric vehicle
From far Asia
And you stay in the zombie house
Experience the pleasure of moaning
Toilets covered in feces
Smell of urine
And itâ€™s spring already people
Birds started singing loud
The sun shines warm liek a mirracle
Encourages for walks
title: Maggot
